  "title": "Export Sales Coordinator #80732",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturer (Commercial Cleaning Equipment)</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Export Sales Coordinator</strong></li><li>Working Location: Gul Crescent (Transport provided)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday-Friday, 8:15AM-5:30PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Handle sales enquiries, prepare quotations, and coordinate order consolidation</li><li>Process customer orders promptly and issue accurate invoices on time.</li><li>Prepare and organize export shipping documents (e.g. bill of lading, packing list, shipping certificate, LC, customs declaration, certificate of origin, marine insurance).</li><li>Provide timely updates on shipment ETD/ETA to all relevant parties.</li><li>Liaise with the Logistics Department on delivery schedules and inventory matters</li><li>Ensure invoices from external service providers (e.g. freight forwarders) are promptly sent to Accounts for processing.</li><li>Assist with warranty and insurance claim processing.</li><li>Maintain accurate records of all sales and shipping documents.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties which may be assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or equivalent qualification.</li><li>Relevant experience in sales support or sales coordination.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80732 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
